{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we marched to the trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Now that was a very bad day for me, because it was a very hot day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was already-- it was already June.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But you're talking about-- I-- I-- I ent-- I arrived to the ghetto approximately on the 16th of May-- 16th or 17th.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And this happened-- when we were marched to the trains, my best guess would-- would have been around-- around the 3rd of June-- 3rd of June, 1944.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We marched to the trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And when we arrived to the station, everything had to be [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Everything has to be done in a terrific hurry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So people had no time to think, and beaten all the time-- beaten with sticks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So quickly into the trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Well, I had no trouble, being-- being 20 year old, 21 year old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But some old people had to be lifted up and thrown in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they kept pressing and pushing, pushing more in and more in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And then it was-- everybody was in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Then-- then they wrote a number on the outside of the cattle wagon-- that 87, or 94, or 79, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "The numbers were around from 75 to 100 in each of these wagons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And then, in the middle of each wagon, they-- usually, they put in a-- a bucket for the toilet purposes, one bucket for 96 people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And-- and if you were lucky-- we had actually a second bucket, which contained cold water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I mean, that-- that was gone in the first 15 minutes, the water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And then they locked the doors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "There was only a very tiny little ventilation window, maybe 15 by 40 centimeters-- something like that-- and very little air in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And it was a hot, very hot, day.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
